Package itb.arkavquarium

Class Aquarium

  • java.lang.Object
    • itb.arkavquarium.Aquarium

  • public class Aquarium
extends java.lang.Object

    Aquarium! The Aquarium class implements and updates all objects in Aquarium. This simulates movement and state of the objects.

    Since:
    2018-04-15
    Version:
    0.0
    Author:
    Abram Situmorang, Faza Fahleraz, Senapati Sang Diwangkara, Yusuf Rahmat Pratama
